Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.96,0:01:09.88,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(994,686)}水母田
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.88,0:01:14.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没捉到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.88,0:01:14.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Missed ya
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.55,0:01:18.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不该在大马路上玩的  小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:18.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't play in the street, little guy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.82,0:01:20.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然会被撞的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.82,0:01:20.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You could get run over
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.89,0:01:27.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,土东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:27.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"The ild ones"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:29.23,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1140,594)}土东西
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.62,0:01:29.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好怪的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.62,0:01:29.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a strange name
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.90,0:01:30.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.90,0:01:30.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Scallop
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.46,0:01:42.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  土东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.46,0:01:42.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye, ild ones
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.02,0:01:44.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喜欢你们呆呆的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.02,0:01:44.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I like your silly name
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.17,0:01:46.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,W
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.17,0:01:46.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"W"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.16,0:01:48.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来他们不是土东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.16,0:01:48.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're not "the ild ones"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.95,0:01:52.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定是坏东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.95,0:01:52.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They must be the wild ones
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.30,0:01:54.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坏东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:54.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The wild ones?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.10,0:01:55.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真该死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:55.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tarnation
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.26,0:01:58.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道坏东西是谁吗  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:01:58.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you know who the wild ones are, son?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.51,0:01:59.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:01:59.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.40,0:02:00.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也不认识你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.40,0:02:00.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know who you are, either
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.67,0:02:06.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们可是海底最残暴嗜血的飞车党
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.67,0:02:03.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, they're the most ferocious
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:06.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,bloodthirsty biker gang under the sea
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.65,0:02:10.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用一个下午就摧毁了整座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.65,0:02:10.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They've destroyed entire cities in an afternoon
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.23,0:02:13.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗜血飞车党
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.23,0:02:13.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bloodthirsty bikers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:19.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1046,716)}裤头村\N{\fnArial}50{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}里
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.94,0:02:16.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们还朝着裤头村过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:16.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And they're headed straight for Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.42,0:02:17.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得去警告大家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.42,0:02:17.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got to warn everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.92,0:02:19.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好走捷径
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:19.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I better take the shortcut
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.46,0:02:21.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.46,0:02:21.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.54,0:02:22.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.54,0:02:22.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.47,0:02:24.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你到底从哪冒出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.47,0:02:24.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where in the blue barnacles did you come from?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.24,0:02:25.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没空问这个了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:25.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no time for that, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.68,0:02:26.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找点重的东西来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:26.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grab something heavy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.70,0:02:27.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,堵住大门
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:27.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bar the door
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.45,0:02:28.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿木板封窗户
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.45,0:02:28.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Board up the windows
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.60,0:02:30.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要保护蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.60,0:02:30.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got to protect the krusty krab
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.28,0:02:34.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡必须活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.28,0:02:34.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krabby Patties must survive
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.60,0:02:38.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别急  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:38.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Settle down, son
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.00,0:02:39.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是发什么神经
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:39.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you all riled up about?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.93,0:02:40.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞车党
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:40.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bikers
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.87,0:02:41.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.87,0:02:41.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,coming
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.75,0:02:42.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,龌龊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.75,0:02:42.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nasty
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.75,0:02:43.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,残暴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.75,0:02:43.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ferocious
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.88,0:02:44.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,占
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.88,0:02:44.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.39,0:02:44.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,领
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:44.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,over
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.92,0:02:45.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,镇子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.92,0:02:45.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,town
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.72,0:02:46.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:46.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Destroy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.80,0:02:47.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:47.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's hide
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.87,0:02:49.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是胡说八道什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:49.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you going on about--
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.37,0:02:50.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞车党吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:50.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,bikers?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.14,0:02:52.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坏东西要来了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:52.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The wild ones are coming, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.80,0:02:56.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们可是全海洋最残暴的饕餮混混
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:54.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're the most vicious, ravenous
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:56.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,horde of hooligans in the sea
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.36,0:02:57.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说饕餮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.36,0:02:57.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Ravenous," did you say?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.40,0:03:00.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以是形容他们贪吃是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:03:00.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's another word for "hungry," isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:03.70,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(702,730)}欢迎坏东西
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.56,0:03:03.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎  坏东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.56,0:03:03.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome, wild ones
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.70,0:03:06.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想把他们轻轻松松引进来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:06.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They'll be drawn here like a sailor to a tattoo parlor
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.03,0:03:09.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就得加个特制摩托停车场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.03,0:03:09.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With a special biker parking
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.87,0:03:12.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有逼真的飞车党装饰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.87,0:03:12.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And authentic biker decor
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.42,0:03:14.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上面有真正的血迹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:14.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With real bloodstains
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.00,0:03:15.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后还有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:15.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And, to top it off
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.32,0:03:17.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,定制摩托堡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.32,0:03:17.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a custom chopper patty
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.45,0:03:18.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最棒的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:18.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And, best of all
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.87,0:03:22.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要涨价150%
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.87,0:03:22.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll raise me prices 150%
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.17,0:03:24.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到时候一定会赚大钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.17,0:03:24.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll make a fortune
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.55,0:03:28.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  事情很严重
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:28.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, this is serious
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.11,0:03:33.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得给那小子放个假
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.11,0:03:33.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That kid needs a vacation--
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.72,0:03:34.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过肯定不带薪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.72,0:03:34.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,unpaid, of course
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:39.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1212,624)}裤头村\N{\fnArial}25{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}里
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.70,0:03:40.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:40.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.86,0:03:43.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:43.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.28,0:03:46.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有一伙叫做坏东西的飞车党要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:46.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A horrible biker gang called the wild ones are coming
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.32,0:03:47.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得马上就跑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:47.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got to run
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.42,0:03:48.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:48.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hide
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.95,0:03:51.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:51.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.05,0:03:52.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听着好严重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.05,0:03:52.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This sounds serious
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.51,0:03:55.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幸好我知道你应该要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.51,0:03:55.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Luckily, I know just what you should do
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.25,0:03:56.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,仔细听好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:56.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen closely
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.16,0:03:59.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓紧你的裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.16,0:03:59.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get a good grip on your pants
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.47,0:04:02.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,转身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:02.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Turn around
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.44,0:04:04.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样吗  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.44,0:04:04.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like this, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.40,0:04:05.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.40,0:04:05.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.35,0:04:11.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:11.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.94,0:04:13.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:13.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.13,0:04:14.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:14.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.00,0:04:15.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有一伙邪恶的飞车党
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:15.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,An evil bunch of bikers
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.35,0:04:17.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要来蹂躏裤头村了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:17.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are coming to ravage Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.34,0:04:20.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  没听到我刚刚说的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:20.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, didn't you hear what I said?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.92,0:04:22.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:22.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I heard you
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.21,0:04:26.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过你好那句我没听到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.21,0:04:26.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But what I didn't hear was a "hello"
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.50,0:04:27.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:27.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.92,0:04:29.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.92,0:04:29.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.42,0:04:31.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗜血飞车党
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:31.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bloodthirsty bikers
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.30,0:04:33.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们必须躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.30,0:04:33.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got to hide
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.76,0:05:05.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:05.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.65,0:05:06.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:06.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I--
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.44,0:05:08.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一点都不想提
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:08.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want to talk about it, man
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.33,0:05:30.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,掩护我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.33,0:05:30.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hide me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.24,0:05:30.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  掩护我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:30.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, hide me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.98,0:05:31.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,掩护我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.98,0:05:31.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hide me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.57,0:05:31.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.57,0:05:31.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.92,0:05:32.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.92,0:05:32.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.43,0:05:32.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:32.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.72,0:05:33.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:33.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.10,0:05:33.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:33.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.44,0:05:33.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.44,0:05:33.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.86,0:05:34.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:34.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.60,0:05:35.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:35.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.44,0:05:36.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别再跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.44,0:05:36.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more running
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.09,0:05:37.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.09,0:05:37.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.60,0:05:40.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那伙飞车党自以为凶狠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:40.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those bikers think they're so tough
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.43,0:05:44.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,穿着皮帽皮裤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.43,0:05:44.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with their leather hats and their leather pants
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.53,0:05:46.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有皮袜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:46.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And their leather socks
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.21,0:05:48.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要是那样子打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.21,0:05:48.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If we dressed up like that
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.40,0:05:51.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是又大又可怕的飞车党了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:51.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then we'd be the big, scary bikers
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.05,0:05:55.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而他们就是幼稚小笨蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.05,0:05:55.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and they'd be little baby doo-doo heads
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.20,0:05:57.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说得太对了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:57.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say that again, Patrick
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:57.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(582,920)}再  说  一  遍
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.52,0:05:59.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幼稚小笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:05:59.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Little baby doo-doo heads
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.09,0:05:59.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.09,0:05:59.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.49,0:06:00.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是那句
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:00.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not that part--
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.29,0:06:03.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是打扮成又大又可怕的飞车党那句
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:03.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the part about dressing up like big, scary bikers
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:06.22,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1122,398)}高菲高伯
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.82,0:06:12.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得怎么样  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:12.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.25,0:06:13.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我样子凶狠不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:13.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do I look tough?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.45,0:06:15.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不会欺负你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.45,0:06:15.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mess with you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.44,0:06:17.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也不会  我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:17.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nor I with you, my friend
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.53,0:06:18.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞车去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.53,0:06:18.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's ride
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.60,0:06:26.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.60,0:06:26.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fear not
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.50,0:06:27.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没必要恐慌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:27.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There is no need to panic
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.15,0:06:31.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村坏小子来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:31.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Bikini Bottom bad boys are here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.56,0:06:34.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这下有安全感了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.56,0:06:34.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel protected now
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.85,0:06:37.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这车看着就挺凶的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:37.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those are some mean-looking rides, dudes
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.83,0:06:40.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:40.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, it's working
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.20,0:06:41.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们以为我们是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:41.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They think we're--
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.82,0:06:42.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,残暴飞车党
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:42.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Vicious bikers
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:47.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(400,438)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:47.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(904,586)}欢迎坏东西
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.17,0:06:50.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村  你们的救星来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:50.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bikini Bottom, your salvation is here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.64,0:06:51.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:51.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.64,0:06:54.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  那是你的口水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:54.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, that's your salivation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:54.30,注释,,0,0,0,,[ salivation（唾液分泌）\N与 salvation（救星）谐音 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.61,0:06:56.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.61,0:06:56.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.54,0:06:58.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你准备好尽自己的本分了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:58.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are you ready to do your part?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.57,0:07:01.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是还要我嘲笑你们两个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.57,0:07:01.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does that part include laughing at you?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.02,0:07:04.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为你们俩样子比平常还要傻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:04.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because you two look even more idiotic than usual
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.26,0:07:07.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们样子不残暴嗜血吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:07.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't we look vicious and bloodthirsty?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.00,0:07:08.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我挺嗜血的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:08.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm bloodthirsty
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:09.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(746,742)}血
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.53,0:07:09.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:09.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.17,0:07:11.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:11.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Want some?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.08,0:07:12.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.08,0:07:12.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.59,0:07:13.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.59,0:07:13.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,thank you, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.26,0:07:14.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只喝无糖的血
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:14.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm drinking diet blood
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:14.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(606,768)}无糖血
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.21,0:07:21.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:21.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.70,0:07:25.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们做一套  真能说一套吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:25.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We walk the walk, but can we talk the talk?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.60,0:07:27.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要不要加入我们的飞车党
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.60,0:07:27.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, you want to join our biker gang?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.92,0:07:29.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:29.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I don't
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.47,0:07:31.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我们的飞车俱乐部呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:31.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about our biker club?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.55,0:07:32.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:32.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.59,0:07:34.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我们的飞车组织呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:34.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about our biker organization?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.45,0:07:35.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:35.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.17,0:07:37.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不要加入你们的飞车联盟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.17,0:07:37.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want to join your biker alliance
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.55,0:07:39.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞车小组  更别提飞车协会了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:39.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your outfit, or your fellowship
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.96,0:07:42.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我们的联合体呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:42.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about our coalition?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.75,0:07:43.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:43.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.64,0:07:45.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,联合体挺排外的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:45.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That one's pretty exclusive
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.65,0:07:48.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,直接把你登记为待定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:48.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll just pencil you down as undecided
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.65,0:07:51.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:51.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.30,0:07:53.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是裤头村坏小子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:53.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're the Bikini Bottom bad boys
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.47,0:07:55.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坏到骨子里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.47,0:07:55.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and we're bad to the bone
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.28,0:07:56.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该挺棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:56.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This should be great
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.66,0:07:58.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到时那伙飞车党肯定能胃口大开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:58.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those bikers can work up an appetite
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.90,0:08:00.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毕竟他们会在停车场暴打你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:08:00.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,beating you up in the parking lot
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.05,0:08:03.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后就会来饱餐一顿美味的蟹黄堡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:03.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then, they can fill up on delicious Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.71,0:08:06.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后再来暴打你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:06.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then, they can beat you up again
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.30,0:08:07.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得了吧  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.30,0:08:07.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.87,0:08:09.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是要赶走那伙飞车党
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.87,0:08:09.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going to run off those bikers
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.65,0:08:11.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拯救蟹堡王的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:11.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and save the krusty krab
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.22,0:08:13.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们休想赶走我的金主顾客
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:13.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not running off any of me paying customers
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.72,0:08:15.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就留着被他们在停车场暴打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:15.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can stay and get beaten up in the parking lot
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.68,0:08:16.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爱走不走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:16.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you wish
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.31,0:08:18.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后我们就能拯救裤头村了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.31,0:08:18.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then can we save the town?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.97,0:08:21.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们就没想过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:21.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Has it ever crossed your mind
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.79,0:08:25.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自己很有可能会白忙活一场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.79,0:08:25.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that you might be getting all worked up over nothing?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.65,0:08:29.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  我什么时候有反应过激过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:29.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, when have I ever been known to overreact?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.41,0:08:30.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.41,0:08:30.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.07,0:08:31.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们餐巾纸没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:31.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're out of napkins
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.79,0:08:34.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,餐巾纸没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.79,0:08:34.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out of napkins
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.70,0:08:36.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:36.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.60,0:08:37.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不小心摘掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:37.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I accidentally removed
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.67,0:08:40.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,床垫上面写着依法不得摘除的标签
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.67,0:08:40.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the "do not remove by penalty of law" tag on my mattress
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.67,0:08:40.55,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 只有厂商不得摘除，消费者可摘除 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.55,0:08:41.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,掩护我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.55,0:08:41.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hide me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.03,0:08:41.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,掩护我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:41.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hide me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.04,0:08:42.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:42.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.96,0:08:43.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:43.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.97,0:08:46.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我瞎了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:46.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've gone blind
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.65,0:08:48.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.65,0:08:48.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.25,0:08:53.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你碰啥事都能过激
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:53.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you always overreact to everything
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.32,0:08:55.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是你众多烦人的特点之一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:55.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's one of your many annoying traits
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.09,0:08:57.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我  烦人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.09,0:08:57.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me, annoying?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.75,0:09:09.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:09.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.39,0:09:13.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说啥都是错的  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.39,0:09:13.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are so wrong about everything, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.36,0:09:16.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只能说唯一完完全全确定的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:16.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that the only thing I am completely sure about
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.79,0:09:20.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有飞车党在朝这边开过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.79,0:09:20.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is that there is no motorcycle gang headed this way
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.51,0:09:23.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:23.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.25,0:09:25.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家注意看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:25.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy, there, mateys
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.55,0:09:28.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一大伙摩托车要开过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:28.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Motorized vehicles coming over the horizon
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.88,0:09:29.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:29.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.36,0:09:30.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:30.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.34,0:09:37.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别光站那啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.34,0:09:37.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there--
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.67,0:09:38.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救救我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:38.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,save us
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.43,0:09:44.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  虽然我知道似乎要完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:44.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, I know this looks like the end
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.05,0:09:45.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我跟你可以共度难关
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.05,0:09:45.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you and I can get through anything
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.89,0:09:48.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要我们能齐心协力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:48.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as long as we do it together
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.73,0:09:49.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:49.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.68,0:09:50.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:50.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:54.74,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1172,210)}公交站
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.25,0:10:06.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只剩咱们俩了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:06.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just you and me, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.25,0:10:08.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我想让你知道  我们能共度难关
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:08.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I want you to know we can get through this
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.45,0:10:09.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.45,0:10:09.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as long as we--
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.42,0:10:11.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恐慌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:11.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Panic
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.04,0:10:12.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快逃命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:12.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run for your lives
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.55,0:10:14.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坏东西要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:14.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The wild ones are coming
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.22,0:10:18.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坏东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:18.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The wild ones?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.76,0:10:20.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,梅布尔  叫小朋友过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:20.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mabel, get the kids
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.76,0:10:23.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亲爱的  我餐巾纸拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:23.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Honey, I got the napkins
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.88,0:10:26.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这回我错过什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.88,0:10:26.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What have I missed this time?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.69,0:10:30.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托  别杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:30.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, don't kill me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.09,0:10:31.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想加入你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.09,0:10:31.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to join you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.62,0:10:35.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一生都梦想着要加入飞车党
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:32.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's been my life-long dream
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:35.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to be a member of a motorcycle gang
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.00,0:10:37.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连坏东西夹克衫我都缝好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:37.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I even knitted my own wild ones jacket
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.91,0:10:41.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要飞车活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.91,0:10:41.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to ride to live
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.20,0:10:43.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我活着就要飞车
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:43.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I live to ride
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.48,0:10:47.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:47.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, spare me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.08,0:10:48.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们要什么  我就做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:48.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll do whatever you want
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.80,0:10:50.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定会背叛我朋友跟邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:50.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll betray my friends and neighbors
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.75,0:10:54.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,饶我一命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:54.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just let me live
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.85,0:10:56.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说什么  小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:56.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that, missy?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.60,0:10:57.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:10:57.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.09,0:10:57.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:10:57.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.22,0:10:59.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:10:59.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're the mild ones
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.76,0:11:01.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:01.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mild
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.00,0:11:01.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.00,0:11:01.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ones?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.47,0:11:06.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把我衣服上的M还回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:06.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me back my "m"
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.00,0:11:09.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大伙儿走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:09.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.13,0:11:11.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们就不想花钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.13,0:11:11.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to spend any money?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.85,0:11:14.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就不想亲亲我裤子后裆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:14.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to kiss the seat of my pants?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.38,0:11:18.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:18.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's ride
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.25,0:11:21.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.25,0:11:21.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-bye
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.90,0:11:23.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们好像还挺和善的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:23.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They seemed really nice
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.15,0:11:25.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.15,0:11:25.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.19,0:11:29.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞车活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.19,0:11:29.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ride to live
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.84,0:11:33.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,活着就飞车
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.84,0:11:33.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and live to ride
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:39.84,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,化敌为友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:42.22,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.74\pos(245.316,450)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:42.22,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.74\pos(495.678,728)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:44.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:44.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.52\pos(393.566,446)}技术总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:44.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.52\pos(519.736,698)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:47.35,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.29\pos(421.602,536)}制片指导
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:47.35,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:49.39,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(244,424)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.30,0:11:50.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.30,0:11:50.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No--
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.96,0:11:52.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.96,0:11:52.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,impossible
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.05,0:11:54.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都数钱数了十几次了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.05,0:11:54.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must have counted me money a dozen times
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.20,0:11:55.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,结果还是少了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:55.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and it still comes up short
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.69,0:11:57.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,利润
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:57.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Profits
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.80,0:11:58.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.80,0:11:58.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.77,0:11:59.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:11:59.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,down
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.55,0:12:03.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真可怜自己
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:03.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for meself
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.93,0:12:05.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这一餐要配饮料吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.93,0:12:05.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you like a drink with that order?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.82,0:12:06.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用  谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:06.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.38,0:12:09.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我进门前就买了杯新上市的海草奶昔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.38,0:12:08.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got me one of those new kelpshakes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:09.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before I came in here
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.04,0:12:11.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总共两块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:11.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That comes out to $2.00 even
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.15,0:12:13.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是实惠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.15,0:12:13.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a steal
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.54,0:12:14.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:14.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the--
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.55,0:12:15.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那家伙怎么没买
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.55,0:12:15.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,why didn't that guy order
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.63,0:12:19.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,汽水机的天价饮料配蟹黄堡吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:17.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a deliciously overpriced fountain beverage
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:19.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with his Krabby Patty?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.05,0:12:22.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我们几天都没卖出一杯汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:22.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, we haven't sold a single soda in days
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.84,0:12:23.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:23.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.72,0:12:24.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:24.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.13,0:12:30.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子  够了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.13,0:12:30.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, boy, it's done
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.70,0:12:33.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再不小心  整杯都会被你吸进食道里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:32.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're going to suck the whole cup down your gullet
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:33.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you're not careful
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.04,0:12:35.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:35.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.45,0:12:38.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是这海草奶昔真是太好喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.45,0:12:38.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just that these kelpshakes taste so good
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:38.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(932,592)}海草奶昔
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.36,0:12:39.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海草奶昔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.36,0:12:39.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kelpshake?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.07,0:12:40.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看你四周
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:40.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look around you
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.24,0:12:43.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都在畅饮美味的海草奶昔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:43.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone's enjoying a delicious kelpshake
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.31,0:12:46.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我马上回来  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:46.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.75,0:12:47.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我去续杯了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.75,0:12:47.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get a refill
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.90,0:12:48.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,续杯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:48.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Refill?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.74,0:12:49.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我得了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:49.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.50,0:12:50.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都听好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:50.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen up, everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.54,0:12:51.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新规定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:51.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,New rule--
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.57,0:12:53.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,严禁外带饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.57,0:12:53.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no outside drinks
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.25,0:12:54.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝不例外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:54.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No exceptions
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.07,0:12:58.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说得好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.07,0:12:58.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's telling 'em
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.45,0:13:01.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我最好去查个水落石出
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:01.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I better get to the bottom of this
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:08.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(710,596)}海草奶昔
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.17,0:13:08.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一家新店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:08.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A new store
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.60,0:13:09.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开在我的地盘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:09.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On my block
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.19,0:13:11.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抢走了我的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.19,0:13:11.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Taking my customers
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.71,0:13:13.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.71,0:13:13.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.65,0:13:15.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的宝贝女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.65,0:13:15.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me own flesh and blood
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.66,0:13:17.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么能这样对你老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.66,0:13:17.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How could you do this to your papa?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.94,0:13:20.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说什么玩意  老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:20.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, dad?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.77,0:13:22.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说的就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:22.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about this
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.65,0:13:25.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一旦品尝到一杯海草奶昔的秘密精华
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:25.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Once you taste the secret goodness of a kelpshake--
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.69,0:13:28.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就肯定会喝上不止一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.69,0:13:28.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't have just one
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.12,0:13:29.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:29.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.42,0:13:31.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自己买去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.42,0:13:31.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Buy your own
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.82,0:13:34.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一分钱都不会给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.82,0:13:34.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, I wouldn't give them a cent
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.36,0:13:36.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真为你遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.36,0:13:36.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.40,0:13:38.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后你就会理解我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.40,0:13:38.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then you do understand me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.85,0:13:39.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:39.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dad
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.77,0:13:41.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你害我丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:41.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're embarrassing me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.92,0:13:44.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:44.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get away
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.55,0:13:46.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:46.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.35,0:13:49.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我诅咒你  新开的海草奶昔店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:49.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Confound you, new kelpshake store
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.35,0:13:50.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有什么秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:50.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's your secret?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.62,0:13:52.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:52.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.80,0:13:54.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:54.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.00,0:13:55.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他一定就是幕后黑手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:55.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I bet he's behind this
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.07,0:13:58.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知道你是幕后黑手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:58.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew you were behind this
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.69,0:13:59.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:13:59.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.88,0:14:01.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没干坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:01.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've done nothing wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.32,0:14:03.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你怎么解释这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:03.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then how do you explain this?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.75,0:14:05.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.75,0:14:05.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holy moly
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.31,0:14:06.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.31,0:14:06.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did that happen?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.20,0:14:07.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,少给我装傻了  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:07.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't try that with me, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.95,0:14:10.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这新店害我生意一落千丈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:10.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This new store is ruining me business
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.05,0:14:11.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:11.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.51,0:14:13.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:13.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.02,0:14:14.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该是我害你没生意才对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.02,0:14:14.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's my job
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.46,0:14:17.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:17.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Blast it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.53,0:14:20.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟这小丑竞争就已经够糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:20.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's bad enough I have to compete with this joker
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.32,0:14:21.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,结果又多了个这玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.32,0:14:21.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, there's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.55,0:14:23.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海草奶昔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.55,0:14:23.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kelpshakes
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.10,0:14:27.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来你并不是幕后黑手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.10,0:14:27.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess you're really not behind this after all
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.42,0:14:28.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:28.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.37,0:14:29.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.37,0:14:29.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They have
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.48,0:14:31.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘密配方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.48,0:14:31.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A secret formula
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.35,0:14:32.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:32.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.45,0:14:33.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别又来个秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:33.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not another secret
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.90,0:14:36.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是有秘密  我就非摸清楚不可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.90,0:14:36.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And if there's a secret, I want to know about it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:43.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1246,748)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.80,0:14:44.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它们在增殖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.80,0:14:44.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're multiplying
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.64,0:14:47.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它们每家街角都开了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:47.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, they're on every corner
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.86,0:14:49.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,个个街区都开了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:49.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Block after block
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.98,0:14:51.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到处都是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.98,0:14:51.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're everywhere
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.79,0:14:55.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须得出手办了这店
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.79,0:14:55.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got to do something about this
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.05,0:14:57.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你确定这样有用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:14:57.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You sure this is going to work?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.60,0:14:58.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,照计划走就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:58.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just stick to the plan
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.54,0:15:04.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:04.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.08,0:15:04.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.08,0:15:04.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:06.51,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(690,808)}仅限员工
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.56,0:15:06.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.56,0:15:06.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.96,0:15:08.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板  我好像找到厨房了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:08.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton, I think I found the kitchen
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.34,0:15:10.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就开搞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:10.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's do this thing
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.30,0:15:11.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:11.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here goes
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.73,0:15:15.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.73,0:15:15.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.52,0:15:16.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.52,0:15:16.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got a little bit of--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:22.10,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(662,244)}好滋味
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.11,0:15:33.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:33.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My eye
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.82,0:15:34.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:34.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My eye
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.37,0:15:35.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:35.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My eye
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.33,0:15:38.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该是甩掉他了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:38.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think we lost him
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.89,0:15:41.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还有没有什么好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.89,0:15:41.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you got any more bright ideas?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.47,0:15:43.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然有了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.47,0:15:43.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course I do
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.63,0:15:48.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好没  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:48.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All set, Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.05,0:15:49.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不信你也得信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:49.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You better believe it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.80,0:15:52.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我发明的这高能机械臂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:52.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This high-powered mechanical bio-arm I invented
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.86,0:15:56.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该轻轻松松就能扒开这餐厅的大门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.86,0:15:56.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,should pry those restaurant doors open nice and easy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.11,0:16:03.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:03.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the barnacles?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.78,0:16:06.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动啊  你这垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.78,0:16:06.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, you piece of garbage
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.29,0:16:08.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.29,0:16:08.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.14,0:16:11.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我投降  我投降
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.14,0:16:11.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Uncle, uncle
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.90,0:16:13.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要想把事情做好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:13.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you want anything done right
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.85,0:16:15.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就得亲自来做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.85,0:16:15.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you got to do it yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.51,0:16:20.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的背
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.51,0:16:20.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me back
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.62,0:16:22.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:22.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.77,0:16:24.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小点声
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.77,0:16:24.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pipe down
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.05,0:16:27.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吵醒看门狗  计划就泡汤了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:27.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're going to soil our plans if you wake the watchdog
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.68,0:16:30.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:30.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never mind that
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.99,0:16:32.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那吵醒海绵宝宝怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.99,0:16:32.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.42,0:16:33.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:33.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.46,0:16:33.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.46,0:16:33.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi--
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.31,0:16:35.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:35.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.68,0:16:38.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我有点搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:38.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, I'm a little confused
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.17,0:16:39.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你跟痞老板不是死对头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.17,0:16:39.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you and Plankton hate each other?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.77,0:16:40.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:40.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course we do
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.68,0:16:41.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:41.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.19,0:16:42.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他咋被你捏拳头里了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:42.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why is he in your fist?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.16,0:16:45.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.16,0:16:45.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.87,0:16:47.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起办商业活动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:47.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gone into business together
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.64,0:16:48.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你说吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:48.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You see, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.82,0:16:50.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们受聘来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:50.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we were hired to, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.86,0:16:52.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,修理这扇门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:52.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,fix this door
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.04,0:16:55.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我们得去修理屋顶了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.04,0:16:55.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now, we have to fix the roof
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.83,0:16:57.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.83,0:16:57.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.24,0:16:57.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:16:57.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.50,0:16:58.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们得去修理屋顶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:58.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got to fix the roof
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.81,0:16:59.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.81,0:16:59.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's--
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.12,0:16:59.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:16:59.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's--
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.44,0:17:00.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,漏水了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.44,0:17:00.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's leaking
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.35,0:17:06.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就祝你们好运
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.35,0:17:06.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, good luck with that
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.14,0:17:07.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:07.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See ya
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.46,0:17:15.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续凿  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.46,0:17:15.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep her going, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.19,0:17:17.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,照这速度  海草奶昔秘方到手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.19,0:17:17.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At this rate, we'll have the kelpshakes recipe
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.65,0:17:19.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定是一眨眼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.65,0:17:19.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,faster than you can say--
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.77,0:17:24.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,离你们自燃还剩三秒钟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:24.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have 3 seconds until spontaneous combustion
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.60,0:17:26.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:26.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's beat it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.95,0:17:27.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.95,0:17:27.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No kidding
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.24,0:17:29.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:29.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.01,0:17:29.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.01,0:17:29.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You forgot--
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.50,0:18:16.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我认输了  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.50,0:18:16.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm throwing in the towel, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.27,0:18:20.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,整了这么多复杂的计划都泡汤了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.27,0:18:20.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All these convoluted plans are getting us nowhere
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.55,0:18:21.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,更有甚者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:21.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And to top it all off
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.91,0:18:24.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出事的就只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:24.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one who's taking the heat
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.29,0:18:26.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你那是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:26.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.12,0:18:28.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都没看到你上前线
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:28.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't see you on the front lines
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.77,0:18:31.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧  那就让我把活都干了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.77,0:18:31.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, let me do all the work
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.17,0:18:34.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你自个袖手旁观当个肥猩猩得了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:34.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,while you just sit back like the fat gorilla you are
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.05,0:18:36.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你管谁叫猩猩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:36.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who are you calling a gorilla
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.72,0:18:39.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你个单细胞独眼底栖生物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:39.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you one-celled, one-eyed bottom-feeder?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.56,0:18:40.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.56,0:18:40.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.51,0:18:42.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想要海草奶昔的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:42.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you want a kelpshake
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.27,0:18:43.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛不直接去买一杯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:43.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,why don't you just buy one?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.56,0:18:45.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,买一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:45.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Buy one?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.52,0:18:50.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来杯海草奶昔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:50.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have one kelpshake, please
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.25,0:18:53.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉这样不太好啊  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:53.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know about this, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.47,0:18:54.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很简单的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:18:54.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's easy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.57,0:18:57.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要微笑  给收银员钱就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:57.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just smile and hand the cashier the money
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.20,0:18:58.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,需要什么服务
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:18:58.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.20,0:18:59.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你好运
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:18:59.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good luck
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.65,0:19:00.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:00.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, there
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.07,0:19:03.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能来杯海草奶昔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:03.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could I get one kelpshake?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.09,0:19:04.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:04.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.77,0:19:05.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总共一块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:05.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That will be $1.00
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.00,0:19:07.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:07.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ok
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.79,0:19:10.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:10.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.59,0:19:14.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:14.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sir?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.29,0:19:16.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请你把钱放开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:16.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please let go of the bill
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.55,0:19:18.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:18.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Release your grip, man
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.67,0:19:19.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:19.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.47,0:19:24.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:24.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enjoy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.47,0:19:25.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:25.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.80,0:19:29.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信我们成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:29.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe we did it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.46,0:19:30.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,信就信吧  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:30.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Believe it, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.75,0:19:32.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱们快去实验室
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:32.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, let's get to the lab
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.44,0:19:34.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,查清楚这东西到底什么成分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:34.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and find out what this stuff is made of
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.49,0:19:43.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面有什么秘密配料  凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:43.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the secret ingredient, Karen?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.82,0:19:47.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看上去主要成分就只是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:47.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it appears that the main ingredient is
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.91,0:19:49.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海草汁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:49.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,kelp juice
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:49.25,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(684,808)}海草汁
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.47,0:19:51.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有海草汁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.47,0:19:51.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just kelp juice?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.20,0:19:53.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来这一直以来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:53.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And to think, this whole time
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.12,0:19:55.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我自个儿就可以卖这玩意了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.12,0:19:55.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could have been selling these meself
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.09,0:19:56.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.09,0:19:56.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.00,0:19:57.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:57.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about me?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.35,0:20:00.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是有谁卖这个赚钱  就该是我才对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.35,0:20:00.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If anyone, I deserve to make a buck selling this stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.67,0:20:02.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想得美  小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.67,0:20:02.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No way, pipsqueak
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.43,0:20:03.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这摇钱树是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:03.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This gold mine is mine
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.80,0:20:05.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我绝不让你得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:05.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not if I can help it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.92,0:20:11.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想得美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.92,0:20:11.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice try
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.38,0:20:13.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要是你  就不会喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:13.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't do that if I were you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.70,0:20:15.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有一样成分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.70,0:20:15.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's another ingredient
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.83,0:20:17.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是我花钱买来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.83,0:20:17.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I paid good money for this thing
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.60,0:20:19.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我当然要喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.60,0:20:19.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course I'm going to drink it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.79,0:20:22.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:22.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the--
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.55,0:20:24.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不懂这玩意有啥了不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.55,0:20:24.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't get what the big deal is
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.72,0:20:26.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,简直跟湿乎乎的运动袜一个味道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:26.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This tastes like a wet gym sock
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.87,0:20:27.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.87,0:20:27.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.83,0:20:29.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我尝尝看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:29.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me try that
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.33,0:20:34.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实还有一小股猛烈的余味
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:34.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, there is a bit of a pungent aftertaste
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.58,0:20:39.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:39.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.62,0:20:40.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还算不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.62,0:20:40.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This ain't half bad
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.30,0:20:44.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是太神了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:44.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is amazing
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.51,0:20:46.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就别独吞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:46.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, don't be selfish
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.15,0:20:51.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.15,0:20:51.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.73,0:20:52.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.73,0:20:52.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.83,0:20:59.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  咱们都喝光了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.83,0:20:59.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabs, we're all out of juice
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.95,0:21:01.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就得再去买
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.95,0:21:01.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then we got to get more
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.70,0:21:03.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们犯了天大的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.70,0:21:03.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're making a big mistake
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.56,0:21:05.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放屁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.56,0:21:05.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Phooey
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.28,0:21:07.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都不知道自己在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:07.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't know what you're talking about
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.67,0:21:09.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海草奶昔  海草奶昔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.67,0:21:09.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kelpshake, kelpshake
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.49,0:21:11.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好爱海草奶昔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:11.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,oh, how I love a kelpshake
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.13,0:21:16.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.13,0:21:16.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's happening to me?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.22,0:21:23.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海草奶昔店都已经关停了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.22,0:21:23.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They've shut down the kelpshakes restaurants
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.89,0:21:28.85,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(794,356)}永久关停
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.93,0:21:33.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,清理这些有害材料要花好几十年
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:31.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It will take decades
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:33.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to clean this hazardous material up
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.10,0:21:37.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真为喝了这玩意的人遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:37.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I sure feel sorry for whoever drank this
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.33,0:21:48.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.33,0:21:48.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at us
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.82,0:21:50.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下我们该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:21:50.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now what are we going to do?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.33,0:21:51.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不知道你要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:51.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know about you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.98,0:21:55.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我要继续做我最拿手的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.98,0:21:55.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'm going back to what I do best--
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.47,0:21:57.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,偷你秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.47,0:21:57.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,stealing your recipe
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.88,0:22:00.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.88,0:22:00.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.67,0:22:01.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.67,0:22:01.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.65,0:22:07.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快到我这来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.65,0:22:07.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come to papa
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.22,0:22:08.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.22,0:22:08.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.93,0:22:10.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你哪都别想去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.93,0:22:10.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not going anywhere
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.02,0:22:13.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让你十秒钟先跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.02,0:22:13.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Without a 10-second head start
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.37,0:22:15.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回家的感觉真好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.37,0:22:15.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's good to be home
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.27,0:22:16.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.27,0:22:16.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You said it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.69,0:22:23.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就爱被人讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.69,0:22:23.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love being hated
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.44,0:22:26.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我回来  你这小鼻屎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.44,0:22:26.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get back here, you little booger
